{"tid":1861752,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【愛的迫降】玄彬為孫藝珍驚喜慶生　IU仗義獻唱OST","createTime":"2020-02-04T09:19:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T16:28:44.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"477ac4158ffa879a152e558adae9f351457fbfa8","tid":1861752,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T09:19:41.000Z","msg":"韓國tvN電視劇《愛的迫降》隨着玄彬（飾演利正赫）到南韓與孫藝珍（飾演尹世理）重逢，劇情開始進入白熱化階段。昨日（2日）播出的第12集《愛的迫降》中，玄彬率領五位秘密到訪南韓的下屬，為孫藝珍送上生日驚喜，令女方感動不已，刺激收視再創新高，達到15.933%，未知即將播出大結局的《愛的迫降》收視會否繼續上升？<br />\n<br />\n另外，韓國傳媒報道，IU將會為《愛的迫降》獻唱OST（原聲帶），因為IU於2015年主演《製作人》，而劇集的編劇正是《愛的迫降》編劇朴智恩，相信 IU是為了支持朴智恩。IU的歌曲和《愛的迫降》OST在音源榜名列前茅，所以IU若確認為獻聲《愛的迫降》，必定成為大熱歌曲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/429550/%E6%84%9B%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%AB%E9%99%8D-%E7%8E%84%E5%BD%AC%E7%82%BA%E5%AD%AB%E8%97%9D%E7%8F%8D%E9%A9%9A%E5%96%9C%E6%85%B6%E7%94%9F-iu%E4%BB%97%E7%BE%A9%E7%8D%BB%E5%94%B1ost\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F429550%2F%25E6%2584%259B%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25BF%25AB%25E9%2599%258D-%25E7%258E%2584%25E5%25BD%25AC%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%25AD%25AB%25E8%2597%259D%25E7%258F%258D%25E9%25A9%259A%25E5%2596%259C%25E6%2585%25B6%25E7%2594%259F-iu%25E4%25BB%2597%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E7%258D%25BB%25E5%2594%25B1ost&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlPMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=137f5997\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/429550/%E6%84%9B%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%AB%E9%99%8D-%E7%8E%84%E5%BD%AC%E7%82%BA%E5%AD%AB%E8%97%9D%E7%8F%8D%E9%A9%9A%E5%96%9C%E6%85%B6%E7%94%9F-iu%E4%BB%97%E7%BE%A9%E7%8D%BB%E5%94%B1ost</a>"},{"pid":"f284c4fb24eac34b7116bbff5f79d0b2276bbcaa","tid":1861752,"uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T09:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/42d38e6678c5149720179c9194258c9c/7216e30237039080-86/s400x600/642d8e25251b103aeb01356215c3685288